  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 130-piece LONDY Luminous Explorer set uses 86 glow rods and 44 black connector balls for night-theme fort builds.",
      "PP rods and connector balls use an insert-and-twist structure, making the set easy to build and take apart.",
      "Packed set price is $23.64. Color box reference is 43 x 28 x 11 cm, with about 3 kg quoted weight.",
      "Space-themed packaging works well for gift shelves, STEM-style building play, and online listings."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "130件 LONDY Luminous Explorer 配置86根夜光杆和44个黑色连接球，主打夜光堡垒搭建。",
      "PP 杆件与连接球采用插入旋转结构，搭建和拆卸都比较方便。",
      "单盒合计价格 $23.64，彩盒参考尺寸为 43 x 28 x 11 cm，报价重量约 3 kg。",
      "太空主题包装适合礼品货架、STEM 拼搭和线上展示。"
    ]
  },
